   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto): ". . . In the matter of the iron, show courage. Give hearty salutations from me to the mother of Komon. And since there is need of it for the fields, do not neglect it. I salute repeatedly Nonna together  with her daughter the nun. I pray for your good health, my lord brother.";(Verso): " Deliver to Agathinos."</ab>
         </div>
